   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-noquest" image="QN_Cl_Leonardo.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="95"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric Leonard</FONT> seems to be looking for you. <BR>Come back after you have speaked to him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-a" mid="6" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What can I do for you?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="5"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard${action:Talk}<BR>Come come, <FONT color=#382000>{user_nick}.</FONT> <BR>I've been waiting for you.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>You're talking about the traitor. Cedric.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="7"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>You are the only one I can ask a favor from. *Sigh*...even if he is a traitor, I couldn't give an order to capture an old friend.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-b" image="QN_Npc_Cl_Fallen_Cedric.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-c" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Shaking off your responsibilities huh? Such a let down.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Yes. You took care of the other traitor, Jake, but <FONT color=#a82424>Cedric</FONT> is still at loose. I've found out he's hiding place, but... I just couldn't bring myself to give an order to the Clerics against him.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-d" mid="12" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Seems like a decent job)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>My apologies if you feel bad. I know how it sounds. But I'm not forcing you. On top of that... I'll pay you well. How does it sound?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-e" mid="16" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Sure.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>...? So, we have a deal?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-accepting-acceptted" mid="18" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>Accept Quest</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$In The Name of Justice$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-1" image="QN_Cl_Tomas.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>I'm leaving it to your hands now. <BR>For more detailed information about Cedric, please look for <FONT color=#a82424>Cleric Thomas</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-a" mid="23" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You lean in closer.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>I believe you've accepted Master Cleric Leonard's request. Come closer.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-b" mid="25" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>I've guessed much, but it's such a humiliation to ask a Sorceress for help.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-b" image="QN_DragonSycophant.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-c" mid="27" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Dragon Follower?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>I must say that Jake was indeed a great Cleric... Who would've thought that he would become a <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT>? It's a tragedy.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-d" mid="29" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>A purpose?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Dragon Followers... They are those who were mesmerized by the power of dragons and worship them as false gods. Of course, it's not as simple as just worshipping. They've formed a confederation, and seem to have a hidden purpose. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-e" mid="31" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>The red-haired girl...</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Their real purpose still remains unknown to me yet, but one thing for sure... It's the power of the <FONT color=#a82424>ancient</FONT> they have their eyes on.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-e" image="QN_Rose.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-f" mid="33" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>I see.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>I'm afraid so. If <FONT color=#a82424>The red-haired girl</FONT> is indeed an ancient, more will seek for her power. <BR>Never can we allow that power to fall into the hands of evil.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-f" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-g" mid="35" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Once we capture that traitor Cedric, the purpose of the Cult's actions will illuminate. According to the information I received, Cedric is hiding in <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT>. Sneak in and bring him back here.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-1-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="36"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>You must take care of this swiftly and remember to stay low-profile.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-2" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="37"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Now, hurry over to <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT> before he evades again.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-a" mid="39" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Well... He's dead.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>How did it go? Did you manage to capture Cedric? Where is he?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-b" mid="41" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Oh no.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="40"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>What? I sent you to capture him, but you have him killed instead!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-c" mid="43" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Well... maybe it's better this way. It would've been difficult to interrogated him for the truth behind the Dragon Followers.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3-c" image="QN_Cl_Leonardo.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="44"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Please inform <FONT color=#a82424>Master Cleric Leonard</FONT> about the news.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-4" image="QN_Cl_Leonardo.dds" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas$<BR>Please inform Master Cleric Leonard about the news.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-a" mid="47" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(You explain the situation)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>So, how did it go?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-b" mid="49" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Both Cedric and Jake suffered the same fate. If possible, I want to save and redeem them... Could this be fate?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-c" mid="51" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Their ideas of justice...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>*Sigh*... I'm sure they had their own ideas of justice. Even though they betrayed the order, they must have followed their hearts. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-d" mid="62" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="61"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Justice is relative. Without power, justice is incompetence and without justice, power is violence. It's human's dilemma to find the balance. I assume their solution was different from ours.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-e" mid="72" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html><FONT color=#086171>(Receive Reward)</FONT></html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="71"><![CDATA[<html>$Quest Reward$</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n011_priest_leonardo-4-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="77"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Cleric Leonard$<BR>Thanks for your help.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
